@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> OnHold : confirm
Approved : entry / log course
OnHold --> Closed : review
OnHold : entry / log course
Closed --> Processing : update
Closed : entry / log course
Processing --> Cancelled : update
Cancelled --> Delivered : confirm
Cancelled : entry / log course
Closed --> Cancelled : revert
Delivered --> [*]
@enduml